{"tid":2129643,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"加害者係唔係永遠都唔會記得自己做過咩事？","createTime":"2020-07-28T17:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:11:36.000Z","uid":225254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcd18caf849280b26fe33db8043345870e55e53","tid":2129643,"uid":225254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:36:30.000Z","msg":"已經係十年前既事，但到今日我仲係活係陰影下。<br />\n加害者仲可以好厚面皮咁關心我既近況，問我係唔係有心事所以訓唔著，有需要可以同佢傾下。<br />\n當我講係因為佢所以訓唔著既時候佢讚我好記性，隔左咁耐都仲記得佢，就好似以前佢對我做既事冇發生過咁。<br />\n我一開始仲天真到以為佢搵我係想同我道歉，但原來佢根本就唔覺得自己有做錯過。<br />\n覺得自己好蠢，十年都走唔到出黎，比一個仆街毀左自己既人生"},{"pid":"51570ee4f1fc3c8a62f207b41a37315982636dbc","tid":2129643,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"綠帽？"},{"pid":"fe1c51808a0fcba8daed1eef67cc8d3c69291095","tid":2129643,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:57:04.000Z","msg":"中學欺凌？"},{"pid":"2cde7b44b826f3e5510e32b956ccf3164b4a5b42","tid":2129643,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1c51808a0fcba8daed1eef67cc8d3c69291095","tid":2129643,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:57:04.000Z","msg":"中學欺凌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:10:53.000Z","msg":",同樣。但我個case係成人欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cda76201966aa7cd00dd3a7b4ad874c78649d2","tid":2129643,"uid":168750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"我成日都話被你依靠，你唔開心可以同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}